---
import SectionHeader from '../ui/SectionHeader.astro';
---

<section id="proces" class="bg-gray-100 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-16">
      <SectionHeader label="JAK DZIAŁAMY" title="Sprawdzony proces,<br />mierzalne rezultaty" />
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-0">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div
        class="flex items-start gap-6 lg:gap-10 py-10 border-b border-gray-300"
        data-reveal="slide-left"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 flex-shrink-0">
          <span
            class="font-display text-[2.5rem] lg:text-[3.5rem] font-black text-accent leading-none italic"
            >01</span
          >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1">
          <h3 class="font-display text-[1.35rem] lg:text-[1.5rem] font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">
            Poznanie potrzeb
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-[1.7] text-[0.95rem] mb-3">
            Poznajemy ofertę, profil i oczekiwania Twojej firmy. Badamy rynek i konkurencję.
            Określamy wspólne cele.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div
        class="flex items-start gap-6 lg:gap-10 py-10 border-b border-gray-300"
        data-reveal="slide-left"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 flex-shrink-0">
          <span
            class="font-display text-[2.5rem] lg:text-[3.5rem] font-black text-accent leading-none italic"
            >02</span
          >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1">
          <h3 class="font-display text-[1.35rem] lg:text-[1.5rem] font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">
            Analiza i audyt
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-[1.7] text-[0.95rem] mb-3">
            Wykonujemy audyt SEO strony. Badamy obszary wymagające poprawy i optymalizacji.
            Analizujemy potencjał ruchu i wzrostów.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div
        class="flex items-start gap-6 lg:gap-10 py-10 border-b border-gray-300"
        data-reveal="slide-left"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 flex-shrink-0">
          <span
            class="font-display text-[2.5rem] lg:text-[3.5rem] font-black text-accent leading-none italic"
            >03</span
          >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1">
          <h3 class="font-display text-[1.35rem] lg:text-[1.5rem] font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">
            Budowa strategii
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-[1.7] text-[0.95rem] mb-3">
            Tworzymy strategię SEO i planujemy poszczególne etapy prac. Dobieramy najlepsze
            dedykowane rozwiązania.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 lg:gap-10 py-10" data-reveal="slide-left">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 flex-shrink-0">
          <span
            class="font-display text-[2.5rem] lg:text-[3.5rem] font-black text-accent leading-none italic"
            >04</span
          >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1">
          <h3 class="font-display text-[1.35rem] lg:text-[1.5rem] font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">
            Prace on-site i off-site
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-[1.7] text-[0.95rem] mb-3">
            Wykonujemy optymalizację: SEO, UX/UI. Uruchamiamy proces link buildingu oraz
            systematycznych działań technicznych i content marketingowych.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 lg:gap-10 py-10" data-reveal="slide-left">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 flex-shrink-0">
          <span
            class="font-display text-[2.5rem] lg:text-[3.5rem] font-black text-accent leading-none italic"
            >04</span
          >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1">
          <h3 class="font-display text-[1.35rem] lg:text-[1.5rem] font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">
            100% SEO
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-[1.7] text-[0.95rem] mb-3">
            Kontynuujemy zaplanowaną strategię SEO. Stale monitorujemy parametry techniczne witryny,
            stan indeksu i odpowiednio reagujemy na zmiany.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
